items.badge_description: So, you're new around here? Congrats on your first brew! This one's for you.

items.checkin_comment: Beautiful spot - no gold on tap but this is actually quite a nice drop. Can’t give it a 5 because it’s not gold, but worth a look anyway if you see it on a tap & there isn’t any gold. The boys are looking good so far go Konstas!
